text: And I think the first part of this issue that should be articulated is AI is kind of a fancy thing. It's first of all, it's two letters. It means artificial intelligence. But ultimately what it is, it's about machine learning. And so the machine is taught. And part of the issue here is what information is going into the machine that will then determine and we can predict then if we think about what information is going in. What then will be produced in terms of decisions and opinions that may be made through that process.
